channel.title: Cant get into my router to portforward
channel.description:
my router is netgear and it seems strange to me but the default gateway is 192.168.1.1 when usually the netgear routers are 192.168.0.1 or somthing like that..
anyways i dont know what type of router it is and i dont know my username and password (have tried defaults)
how do i find what type of router it is and my username and password?
